id: "class:fighter#weapon_master"
name: "Weapon Master"
description: "Devoted to the perfection of a single weapon, the weapon master's meditations\
  \ upon his favored weapon border on the obsessive, but none can deny his consummate\
  \ skill. The weapon master must select a single type of weapon (such as longsword\
  \ or shortbow). All of his abilities apply to that weapon type."
